2055466993.text: "Platelet survival is extended in mice lacking the pro apoptotic proteins Bak and Bax, whereas platelet clearance is accelerated in mice lacking the pro survival proteins Bcl-2, Bcl-xL, and Mcl-1, and in mice treated with the BH3 mimetic ABT-737 (inhibitor of pro survival Bcl-2, Bcl-xL, and Bcl-w)."
